  { question: 'What metrics matter for print-on-demand stores?', answer: 'Margin per email order, Trend drop sell-through, Personalization completion rate, Discount dependency ratio' },
  { question: 'When is tool sprawl risky for print-on-demand stores?', answer: 'When popup, email, SMS, reviews, and loyalty each send conflicting offers without shared suppressions — common when segments overlap.' },
