  { question: 'Should trend drops use Privy or Sequenzy?', answer: 'Privy for capture on trend landing pages; Sequenzy for drop sequencing and post-purchase personalization follow-up. Trend drop sell-through improves when VIP gates precede public blasts — not when three apps send independently.' },
