      <p><strong>Scenario B — Personalized mug store, high cart abandon on custom text.</strong> Personalization follow-up recovered 14% of half-finished designs — distinct from standard cart recovery. Personalization completion rate became the optimization target, not generic open rate.</p>
      <p><strong>Scenario C — Creator community POD, audience-owned designs.</strong> Community content emails outperformed product promos 2:1 on repeat purchase. Creator and niche community content built trust; Privy captured on creator landing pages fed Sequenzy lifecycle without discount escalation on day one.</p>
