      <p>POD margins cannot absorb collision damage from welcome discounts, cart recovery, trend drops, and site-wide sales stacking.</p>
      <p><strong>Trend drop week:</strong> Pause winback discount branches. Public sale suppresses for VIP early-access cohort until drop sells through.</p>
      <p><strong>Personalization abandon + cart recovery:</strong> One recovery owner — dual emails with different discounts on same design destroy margin and trust.</p>
      <p><strong>Creator collab launch:</strong> Community announcement owns inbox — generic clearance must pause 72 hours.</p>
      <p><strong>Post-purchase:</strong> Cross-sell complementary designs at full price before any winback discount — impulse buyers rebuy quickly if product delivered well.</p>
